<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df62eb79dbc410ad64efc6edc9917ac62a716616","tid":541634,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"TPP協議曾經被認為是美國在太平洋地區孤立中國的一大重大的經濟與政治策略，曾經引發北京方面的強烈關注。<br />\n<br />\n而美國總統特朗普上任之後宣布美國推出TPP協定的決議也被專家們解讀為是美國外交政策的一大失算，將把美國在太平洋地區的影響力拱手讓給了中國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過，在日本等國的推動下，TPP似乎起死回生，尤其是加拿大近日將正在積極推動TPP協定的簽署。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3883e67d5f81a8c00689e0623e4f8516589a84c","tid":541634,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"由前方箭頭變後衛大腳助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fdd74760f23f03d182098f433daf98c38db61a","tid":541634,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c48429ff3065203976f14d84bc9dd6cfbda1cfe","tid":541634,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8390c06d2a421d010031333a54585da4b993703","tid":541634,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開全力郁中國<br />\n<br />\nJR堆撚樣講兩句？<br />\n唔係話美國唔夠膽郁中國咩？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:44:27.000Z","msg":"邊撚個JR？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e885b40a116af3003ea84ace75a6a710caa4f0f9","tid":541634,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"圍堵支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786286b3f8e1cbe274640b751afe0e97319a4e2c","tid":541634,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"同之前果個有咩分別<img src